-- G20 source: Agreement on way to highlight economic risks
-- 
-- Fri Apr 15, 2011 4:50pm EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/04/15/us-g20-imbalances-idUSTRE73D25E20110415

 

 WASHINGTON  (Reuters) - Top world economies have agreed on the use of indicators to highlight national economic policies that could pose a threat to the global economy, a Group of 20 official said on Friday. 

 One issue that remained undecided was whether to name the countries that fall foul of the new guidelines at this stage, said the official, who spoke on the condition of not being identified. (Writing by  William Schomberg ; Editing by Leslie Adler)